display_name: For women: Intro to Coding Workshop
text:
\*FOR WOMEN ONLY\*

Are you a female immigrant or refugee who is curious to know more about coding? This presentation is for you!

Join us at Futurekids in Lausanne on Monday January 27th from 1.30pm to 4.00pm! The event is FREE - sign up now!
